{"id":431083,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":5,"day":27}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"343","ytitle":"","mtitle":"上海抒情","ftitle":"","authors":["顾工"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我推开我的楼窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个上海展现眼底；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们翻越无数雪山峻岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才登上你巍峨的屋宇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄浦江的水啊!吴淞口的帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南京路的灯啊!百万人的笑语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都滚滚涌进我的胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的血管中循环不息!……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外白渡桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外白渡桥啊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前是个弯曲的背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远洋来的一群群酒鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用皮靴敲打你的脊椎!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外白渡桥啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天是高扬起来的眉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用黄浦江的波光眺望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民的身影多么健美!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我性的这所小楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有一位诗人被捕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派用黑色的子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射碎他心灵的窗户!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我在他的窗台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插上红花一束，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让社会主义阳光照耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也浇洒上诗的露珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用多少支斗争火把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃了今天灿烂的灯光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从长安街到南京路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处是欢乐的人影在交往……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了灯光不能忘记火把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能在幸福的街头迷惘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让斗争的火把永在心头燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让灯盏都化为太阳照红心房。"}]}